resources.string: Kuv lub npe hu ua Amanda.
Yog tias koj tab tom txaus siab rau cov app no Kuv tsim, thov xav yuav kuv cov khoom pub dawb.
Lub vev xaib pub dawb tsis tau ua dab tsi, tab sis koj txoj kev pub dawb yuav qhia kuv tias kuv lub sijhawm siv sijhawm los tsim kho dawb, tsis muaj kev tshaj tawm cov apps.
Yog tias koj tab tom txaus siab rau cov app no Kuv txhim kho, thov xav yuav kuv qhov upgrade app.

Cov khoom siv hloov tshiab suav nrog lub thawv rau kev khij thaum koj tsis dhau daim nqi lossis nyiaj npib, thiab koj qhov kev yuav khoom yuav qhia kuv tias kuv lub sijhawm siv sijhawm txhim kho dawb, tsis muaj tshaj tawm cov apps.
